{"tid":627554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西九龍中心水晶店男東主 遭女子淋腐液","createTime":"2018-04-13T05:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T05:25:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"508d4db91b80a00adeffa3b233dee920179462e7","tid":627554,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360567?_ga=2.137415472.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360567%3F_ga%3D2.137415472.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=PIP6CtNqzdV40iPEgTS2v%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=96d758f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180413%2F20360567%3F_ga%3D2.137415472.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=93357ee6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180413/20360567?_ga=2.137415472.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n西九龍中心水晶店男東主<br />\n遭女子淋腐液<br />\n<br />\n5.4K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗西九龍中心，昨晚近8時，一名戴口罩女子闖入商場7樓一間水晶店，向57歲姓林男東主淋潑懷疑腐液，男店主走避不及，全身均被液體濺中，女兇徒事後逃去無蹤，事主負傷自行報警求助。救護員接報到場，將傷者送往明愛醫院治理。警方初步相信作淋潑傷者的是通渠水，正調查女兇徒的動機，以及追緝其歸案。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，遭淋腐液的男店東稱無與人結怨，亦無欠倩，未知遇襲原因。"}]}